1
00:00:15,809 --> 00:00:21,247
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:22,082 --> 00:00:29,989
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:30,056 --> 00:00:35,426
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:35,495 --> 00:00:39,556
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:45,703
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:46,439 --> 00:00:53,345
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:54,748 --> 00:00:58,240
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:58,318 --> 00:01:05,281
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:05,358 --> 00:01:12,423
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:12,499 --> 00:01:19,166
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:19,639 --> 00:01:29,139
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:30,863 --> 00:01:32,524
Who're you guys?

13
00:01:59,992 --> 00:02:02,017
I'm in a bad mood right now.

14
00:02:03,762 --> 00:02:05,354
If you wanna continue to fight,

15
00:02:05,931 --> 00:02:07,455
I won't go easy on you.

16
00:02:11,136 --> 00:02:15,163
You stop your babbling, weakling.

17
00:02:17,442 --> 00:02:19,239
Hey, come over here.

18
00:02:20,179 --> 00:02:22,704
I'm gonna play
do re mi fa so la ti do on you...

19
00:02:22,781 --> 00:02:24,078
while I snap your ribs!

20
00:02:25,117 --> 00:02:26,141
I'll do it!

21
00:02:40,799 --> 00:02:43,359
<i>What?! He got both of my legs</i>
<i>with his string...!</i>

22
00:02:53,011 --> 00:02:54,069
Why you!

23
00:03:00,052 --> 00:03:03,044
Humph! Let's hear a nice sound.

24
00:03:03,121 --> 00:03:04,019
Do!

25
00:03:06,024 --> 00:03:07,616
<i>W-What?!</i>

26
00:03:08,594 --> 00:03:09,424
Re!

27
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:17,530
<i>Wh-Where is he attacking from?!</i>

28
00:03:20,038 --> 00:03:23,633
Your bones make
a really low sound, don't they?

29
00:03:25,077 --> 00:03:27,545
Let's hear a much sharper reverberation,
shall we?

30
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:29,210
Right?

31
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:57,440
Next, I'll go for
a mi fa so tri combination.

32
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:03,112
Wha?!

33
00:04:07,886 --> 00:04:08,614
What?!

34
00:04:15,894 --> 00:04:16,986
Last!

35
00:04:19,698 --> 00:04:20,756
Lions Barrage!

36
00:04:22,734 --> 00:04:28,468
<i>An Invitation from the Sound</i>

37
00:04:28,807 --> 00:04:29,933
Here you are!

38
00:04:30,075 --> 00:04:32,043
I'm digging in!

39
00:04:34,713 --> 00:04:37,204
Sakura! Go on, eat, eat!

40
00:04:37,549 --> 00:04:40,950
The Chinese style barbecued pork
ramen noodles here are fabulous!

41
00:04:43,021 --> 00:04:46,115
Don't worry. It's my treat.

42
00:04:46,191 --> 00:04:47,522
Right, chef?

43
00:04:48,226 --> 00:04:49,784
You're gonna treat your girl.

44
00:04:49,861 --> 00:04:51,920
You're growing up, aren't you, Naruto?

45
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:54,225
Wh-Wh-What?!

46
00:04:54,299 --> 00:04:56,028
Wh-What the heck are
you talking about?

47
00:04:56,101 --> 00:04:59,434
I need to have an important conversation
with Sakura today...

48
00:04:59,504 --> 00:05:01,904
Sh-She's not my girl
or anything like that...

49
00:05:03,008 --> 00:05:04,202
Sakura?

50
00:05:06,411 --> 00:05:09,403
Sorry, Naruto. I was little spaced out.

51
00:05:10,582 --> 00:05:11,947
This looks delicious.

52
00:05:12,751 --> 00:05:14,309
Now then... Let's eat! Let's eat!

53
00:05:14,786 --> 00:05:19,189
Yeah! Tell me about Sasuke
while we eat.

54
00:05:39,311 --> 00:05:43,714
Sasuke told me not to tell you this,
Naruto, but...

55
00:05:56,128 --> 00:05:59,120
It's all that guy Orochimaru's fault...

56
00:06:04,703 --> 00:06:06,933
<i>S-Stop!</i>

57
00:06:14,646 --> 00:06:19,447
Kakashi Sensei said it would be fine
and I'd like to believe that too...

58
00:06:20,385 --> 00:06:23,354
But when he was battling Gaara...

59
00:06:30,996 --> 00:06:32,463
Earlier today...

60
00:06:32,531 --> 00:06:34,863
Sasuke was wearing the same expression
as the time before.

61
00:06:35,467 --> 00:06:36,957
That's why I...

62
00:06:43,809 --> 00:06:48,439
Orochimaru, huh?
I ran into him again a little while back.

63
00:06:48,747 --> 00:06:50,476
Really? Where?!

64
00:06:51,550 --> 00:06:54,212
When I was searching for
Old Lady Tsunade...

65
00:06:57,956 --> 00:06:58,888
<i>Die!</i>

66
00:07:02,127 --> 00:07:02,957
Shoot!

67
00:07:13,638 --> 00:07:15,572
Pervy Sage and the old lady...

68
00:07:15,740 --> 00:07:17,367
Despite the fact that
he was fighting two of them at once,

69
00:07:17,442 --> 00:07:19,069
he was incredibly powerful.

70
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,574
He's one dangerous dude.

71
00:07:24,115 --> 00:07:25,139
That strong...

72
00:07:26,318 --> 00:07:28,081
It'll all be fine, believe it!

73
00:07:29,721 --> 00:07:33,179
Sasuke wouldn't fall to
that kind of guy's enticement.

74
00:07:33,391 --> 00:07:35,086
He's already a really powerful guy,

75
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:37,287
so he wouldn't need to do
that kind of thing

76
00:07:41,333 --> 00:07:42,994
I guarantee it!

77
00:07:50,542 --> 00:07:51,201
Yeah!

78
00:07:59,918 --> 00:08:04,719
Why does Master Orochimaru
want this guy anyway?

79
00:08:05,957 --> 00:08:08,687
Kimimaro would have
been much better...

80
00:08:12,063 --> 00:08:15,555
Well, if you stay in
a seedy place like this,

81
00:08:15,634 --> 00:08:18,467
you'll just remain mediocre at best.

82
00:08:19,337 --> 00:08:21,032
You'll never become strong...

83
00:08:21,506 --> 00:08:23,201
<i>Wh-Why...?</i>

84
00:08:23,608 --> 00:08:27,305
<i>All my barrages were solid.</i>
<i>Yet this guy...</i>

85
00:08:27,379 --> 00:08:29,108
<i>doesn't seem to have</i>
<i>sustained any damage.</i>

86
00:08:30,815 --> 00:08:33,784
If you keep on fooling around
playing Ninja with your friends,

87
00:08:33,852 --> 00:08:36,116
you're just gonna continue to rot.

88
00:08:39,224 --> 00:08:40,623
Come with us.

89
00:08:41,226 --> 00:08:45,356
If you do,
Master Orochimaru will empower you.

90
00:08:50,869 --> 00:08:53,497
There's no meaning
if we take you by force, he said.

91
00:08:55,006 --> 00:08:56,530
You decide.

92
00:08:58,243 --> 00:08:59,335
Gimme a break...

93
00:08:59,411 --> 00:09:01,606
Master Orochimaru sure sent me
on a bothersome mission.

94
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,874
Hey! What did you decide?

95
00:09:04,049 --> 00:09:05,380
Are you coming?

96
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:06,474
Or are you not coming?!

97
00:09:09,854 --> 00:09:11,446
Decide already!

98
00:09:13,858 --> 00:09:16,292
When a weakling like you lags,

99
00:09:16,361 --> 00:09:17,953
it makes me wanna just finish you!

100
00:09:19,831 --> 00:09:21,196
Try me...!

101
00:09:30,942 --> 00:09:33,638
You... those Curse Marks...

102
00:09:45,624 --> 00:09:47,023
Don't be so sure that

103
00:09:47,092 --> 00:09:50,152
you're the only favorite
of Master Orochimaru.

104
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:54,599
One shouldn't use Curse Marks
that lightly.

105
00:09:55,233 --> 00:09:59,693
Or rather... it looks like you're not
even able to control the Curse Marks.

106
00:10:00,839 --> 00:10:03,501
If they continue to be released
for a long period of time,

107
00:10:03,575 --> 00:10:06,442
Curse Marks will progressively
eat your body.

108
00:10:07,112 --> 00:10:09,706
It looks like you're still at first state,

109
00:10:09,781 --> 00:10:12,011
so the speed at which they will
eat away at you is still fairly slow.

110
00:10:12,784 --> 00:10:14,684
But when they have entirely eaten you,

111
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:17,251
you will lose yourself.

112
00:10:17,789 --> 00:10:19,086
Forever.

113
00:10:23,528 --> 00:10:25,621
In exchange for having been
empowered by Curse Marks,

114
00:10:25,697 --> 00:10:27,756
you will be tethered
by Master Orochimaru.

115
00:10:28,066 --> 00:10:30,364
We no longer have anything
like freedom.

116
00:10:31,536 --> 00:10:34,835
In order to receive something,
one must discard something.

117
00:10:36,608 --> 00:10:38,508
What is your objective?

118
00:10:39,044 --> 00:10:41,171
Are you and your comrades
just going to comfort each other

119
00:10:41,246 --> 00:10:42,907
in this lukewarm village...

120
00:10:43,381 --> 00:10:45,110
then simply forget all about...

121
00:10:45,850 --> 00:10:47,647
Itachi Uchiha?

122
00:10:51,022 --> 00:10:52,785
Don't forget your objective.

123
00:10:54,192 --> 00:10:57,161
This kind of village does
nothing more than shackle you!

124
00:10:57,862 --> 00:11:01,161
Cut your stupid ties with this place.

125
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:03,390
If you do that, you'II...

126
00:11:04,302 --> 00:11:07,430
be able to obtain much,
more fabulous power.

127
00:11:08,506 --> 00:11:09,973
Don't forget your objective!

128
00:11:36,167 --> 00:11:37,191
Thanks!

129
00:11:37,335 --> 00:11:38,893
H-Hey Sakura.

130
00:11:39,104 --> 00:11:40,401
I'll walk you home!

131
00:11:40,839 --> 00:11:41,897
Huh? Don't worry about it.

132
00:11:41,973 --> 00:11:45,374
Why, why?
The streets are dangerous at night!

133
00:11:47,479 --> 00:11:49,709
They're well lit, so I'll be fine...

134
00:11:57,422 --> 00:11:58,354
Sakura?

135
00:12:00,558 --> 00:12:01,855
Thanks, Naruto.

136
00:12:02,727 --> 00:12:04,854
But I want to go home alone tonight.

137
00:12:05,764 --> 00:12:06,696
I see...

138
00:12:07,732 --> 00:12:08,699
I'll be fine!

139
00:12:10,235 --> 00:12:10,860
Yeah!

140
00:13:47,565 --> 00:13:51,296
Why are you hanging around in a place
like this in the middle of the night?

141
00:13:52,937 --> 00:13:55,735
One has to pass down this road
to leave the village

142
00:13:58,243 --> 00:13:59,175
Go home and sleep.

143
00:14:13,925 --> 00:14:15,017
Why...

144
00:14:16,628 --> 00:14:18,653
Why won't you tell me anything?

145
00:14:20,164 --> 00:14:21,529
Why are you always silent like that?

146
00:14:22,934 --> 00:14:24,424
You won't tell me one single thing.

147
00:14:24,502 --> 00:14:26,629
Why should I have to tell you anything?!

148
00:14:29,674 --> 00:14:31,642
I'm telling you to keep your nose
out of my business.

149
00:14:32,610 --> 00:14:34,373
Stop bothering me
over everything I do.

150
00:14:38,249 --> 00:14:42,583
I... make you dislike me
all the time, don't I?

151
00:14:45,757 --> 00:14:46,655
Do you remember?

152
00:14:47,959 --> 00:14:52,089
We just became Genin and
the Three-Man Squads were assigned...

153
00:14:53,298 --> 00:14:56,631
You and I were alone for
the first time, here at this very spot.

154
00:14:58,436 --> 00:14:59,835
You got mad at me.

155
00:15:00,371 --> 00:15:03,169
<i>See! That guy doesn't</i>
<i>have parents, right?</i>

156
00:15:03,775 --> 00:15:07,336
<i>He's all alone and he doesn't have to deal</i>
<i>with parents lecturing him...</i>

157
00:15:07,412 --> 00:15:09,812
<i>That's why he can sometimes</i>
<i>be selfish!</i>

158
00:15:12,183 --> 00:15:13,115
<i>Solitude...</i>

159
00:15:13,351 --> 00:15:14,181
<i>Huh?</i>

160
00:15:15,853 --> 00:15:18,754
<i>Isn't the same as being scolded</i>
<i>by one's parents.</i>

161
00:15:19,824 --> 00:15:21,382
<i>What's the matter all of a sudden...</i>

162
00:15:23,194 --> 00:15:25,162
<i>You...are annoying...</i>

163
00:15:41,212 --> 00:15:42,474
I don't remember that.

164
00:15:49,220 --> 00:15:52,883
Yeah, I guess...
that was long ago, after all...

165
00:15:54,025 --> 00:15:56,323
But it all began that day.

166
00:15:56,995 --> 00:15:58,462
Sasuke and me...

167
00:15:59,597 --> 00:16:02,862
And also Naruto and Kakashi Sensei...

168
00:16:25,189 --> 00:16:27,248
The four of us went
on various missions, didn't we?

169
00:16:29,327 --> 00:16:32,990
Those were tough and
difficult times, but...

170
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:43,572
But...

171
00:16:46,277 --> 00:16:47,437
more than anything...

172
00:16:56,487 --> 00:16:57,749
it was so much fun!

173
00:17:05,296 --> 00:17:07,628
I know about your family, Sasuke...

174
00:17:08,132 --> 00:17:10,566
But revenge...

175
00:17:12,637 --> 00:17:14,628
that won't bring anyone happiness.

176
00:17:16,074 --> 00:17:17,234
No one...

177
00:17:18,810 --> 00:17:20,141
Neither you...

178
00:17:22,647 --> 00:17:23,773
nor I.

179
00:17:26,551 --> 00:17:27,745
As I expected...

180
00:17:31,122 --> 00:17:32,885
I'm different from you guys...

181
00:17:33,791 --> 00:17:36,316
I'm walking a road that's incompatible
with the rest of you.

182
00:17:37,628 --> 00:17:38,993
The four of us worked together...

183
00:17:39,697 --> 00:17:43,531
and it's true that there was a time
when I thought that was my road.

184
00:17:44,769 --> 00:17:46,566
The four of us have worked together,

185
00:17:46,637 --> 00:17:49,037
but in the end,
I decided on revenge.

186
00:17:51,476 --> 00:17:53,467
That's been my reason for living.

187
00:17:57,415 --> 00:17:59,645
I can't become like
you and Naruto.

188
00:18:00,184 --> 00:18:02,778
Are you going to isolate
yourself again, Sasuke?!

189
00:18:03,421 --> 00:18:06,754
You taught me that solitude
is a very rough thing that time, Sasuke!

190
00:18:07,959 --> 00:18:09,984
Now I know exactly how that feels.

191
00:18:10,995 --> 00:18:13,725
I have both family and friends...

192
00:18:14,265 --> 00:18:17,325
But if you were no longer here, Sasuke...

193
00:18:18,436 --> 00:18:19,334
for me...

194
00:18:20,571 --> 00:18:24,337
for me it would be the same as solitude.

195
00:18:30,882 --> 00:18:32,144
From here again...

196
00:18:33,684 --> 00:18:36,346
we're going to start walking
our new paths individually.

197
00:18:36,521 --> 00:18:37,317
I...!

198
00:18:38,289 --> 00:18:41,087
I love you so very, very much, Sasuke!

199
00:18:42,193 --> 00:18:44,525
If you would only be with me, Sasuke,

200
00:18:44,595 --> 00:18:46,654
I won't let you regret it,
no matter what!

201
00:18:46,797 --> 00:18:50,893
I'll make it fun every day and
you will definitely find happiness!

202
00:18:51,969 --> 00:18:54,938
I'll do anything for you, Sasuke!

203
00:18:55,606 --> 00:18:59,098
So... I'm begging you,
please stay here!

204
00:19:00,378 --> 00:19:01,970
I'll even help you with your revenge!

205
00:19:02,747 --> 00:19:05,238
I'll make it happen somehow,
I promise you...!

206
00:19:05,716 --> 00:19:09,311
So stay here... with me...!

207
00:19:12,223 --> 00:19:13,690
If that doesn't work for you...

208
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:18,351
Then take me with you...

209
00:19:26,137 --> 00:19:29,231
You really are... annoying.

210
00:19:33,044 --> 00:19:34,170
Don't go.

211
00:19:35,646 --> 00:19:37,841
If you go, I'll scream and...

212
00:19:44,589 --> 00:19:45,385
Sakura...

213
00:19:51,062 --> 00:19:51,858
Thank you...

214
00:20:05,910 --> 00:20:08,504
<i>Sasuke...</i>

215
00:20:23,294 --> 00:20:25,785
We were waiting for you, Master Sasuke.

216
00:20:28,232 --> 00:20:30,166
What's your intention?

217
00:20:31,302 --> 00:20:33,896
It was already decided that
you would be our leader

218
00:20:33,971 --> 00:20:37,099
the moment you exited the village

219
00:20:38,075 --> 00:20:40,873
Please forgive our rudeness
up to now.

220
00:20:46,117 --> 00:20:47,812
I don't care about any of that.

221
00:20:53,991 --> 00:20:55,117
Let's go.

222
00:21:02,333 --> 00:21:03,357
This is the beginning!

223
00:21:13,678 --> 00:21:20,777
<i>Once in a long while, once in a while</i>

224
00:21:20,918 --> 00:21:26,447
<i>The remnants of a person</i>
<i>broken by dreams</i>

225
00:21:26,624 --> 00:21:31,687
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

226
00:21:34,999 --> 00:21:41,996
<i>Clinging to the Divine,</i>
<i>clinging to Buddha</i>

227
00:21:42,073 --> 00:21:47,602
<i>The remnants of a person crying</i>

228
00:21:48,012 --> 00:21:51,573
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

229
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:56,310
<i>Rendezvous with a happy dance circle</i>

230
00:21:56,387 --> 00:22:00,187
<i>This is my victory pose, round and around</i>
<i>(round around)</i>

231
00:22:00,524 --> 00:22:03,459
<i>Shake shake shake</i>
<i>Let's look</i>

232
00:22:03,527 --> 00:22:07,657
<i>With a bye bye rhythm that never ends</i>

233
00:22:16,841 --> 00:22:21,938
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

234
00:22:23,881 --> 00:22:27,146
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

235
00:22:27,551 --> 00:22:30,748
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

236
00:22:31,021 --> 00:22:35,014
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

237
00:22:38,829 --> 00:22:41,457
What? That jerk Sasuke.

238
00:22:41,632 --> 00:22:45,090
What the heck is he thinking?
He has such a twisted personality!

239
00:22:45,169 --> 00:22:47,865
What is it that he disliked so much
that he'd do something like this?!

240
00:22:48,072 --> 00:22:52,475
Damn! I'm not about to let that guy
do whatever he wants!

241
00:22:52,877 --> 00:22:55,505
If things come to this, I'll chase him
down to the end of the world.

242
00:22:55,679 --> 00:22:59,115
I'll drag that guy back
even if I have to grab him by his neck!

243
00:23:00,017 --> 00:23:03,145
Next time:
"Formation! The Sasuke Retrieval Squad!"
